------------CAO Semester Project----------------

This is a Water level monitoring system. 
The system alarms when the water level increases from a certain level.

ESP-32, LED lights, buzzer and Ultra-sonic sensor were used in this project.

A green light turns on when the bucket is empty i.e when the water level is low. 
A red light turns on along with the buzzer when the water crosses a certain height.

USE: 
  This can be helpful in common household to alram the residents when the water tank is either about to go empty or when the water tank is about to overflow.
